This is a firebreath NPAPI plugin project - to compile the plugin, download firebreath (http://code.google.com/p/firebreath/downloads/detail?name=firebreath-1.1.0.tar.bz2), extract, and link this directory to
/path/to/firebreath/projects/gpgAuthPlugin

then cd to /path/to/firebreath/ and run `makeprep.sh`

then cd to /path/to/firebreath/build

and type `make`

Library dependencies:
    libgpgme11-dev

To compile only the gpgAuth library, cd to /path/to/firebreath/projects/gpgAuthPlugin and execute

`g++ -lgpgme -lgpg-error gpgauth.cpp -o gpgauth`

then execute ./gpgauth

